But why  here?

15:30.597 --> 15:32.223
Because this is

15:30.597 --> 15:32.223
the only guy I know

15:32.265 --> 15:33.974
that would trade

15:32.265 --> 15:33.974
a job interview

15:34.016 --> 15:35.602
