Greetings, Earthlings.

15:39.021 --> 15:41.190
You've got to

15:39.021 --> 15:41.190
be kidding me.

15:41.232 --> 15:43.192
Trust me, I know

15:41.232 --> 15:43.192
it's going to be hard,

15:43.234 --> 15:45.361
but if you can just

15:43.234 --> 15:45.361
keep your mouth shut

15:45.403 --> 15:47.988
for five minutes with this guy,

15:45.403 --> 15:47.988
you're home free.

15:48.030 --> 15:49.990
I'm waiting, princess.

15:50.032 --> 15:51.659
(growling)

15:57.039 --> 15:58.792
My résumé.

15:58.833 --> 16:01.001
(chuckles)

15:58.833 --> 16:01.001
Forget this.

