Well, I...

16:11.053 --> 16:14.641
Interesting. You know,

16:11.053 --> 16:14.641
I like to think of Lucky Aide

16:14.682 --> 16:17.393
as a kind of family,

16:14.682 --> 16:17.393
and in this family,

16:17.435 --> 16:18.853
I'd be your father,

16:18.895 --> 16:20.271
and as a father,

16:20.313 --> 16:21.689
there might be things

16:21.731 --> 16:23.650
I might ask of you

16:21.731 --> 16:23.650
that don't make sense,

16:23.691 --> 16:26.277
but you do it because

16:23.691 --> 16:26.277
I'm your father.

16:26.319 --> 16:29.029
No sassing back, just do it.

16:29.071 --> 16:30.281
Understand?

