Think so.

16:35.077 --> 16:36.036
Now,

16:36.078 --> 16:38.247
who are  you  in this family?

16:39.081 --> 16:41.041
Are you the second cousin?

16:41.083 --> 16:43.544
Or maybe the kooky aunt?

16:48.090 --> 16:51.469
Well, you know, I've always

16:48.090 --> 16:51.469
kind of seen myself

16:51.511 --> 16:55.222
in the role

16:51.511 --> 16:55.222
of the younger brother--

16:55.264 --> 16:56.975
eager to learn.

16:57.016 --> 16:59.268
I never had a brother.

