17:15.618 --> 17:18.078
without any Camembert?

17:18.120 --> 17:20.080
That ruins

17:18.120 --> 17:20.080
my entire aesthetic!

17:20.122 --> 17:22.000
Francis...

17:20.122 --> 17:22.000
Forget it.

17:22.041 --> 17:24.043
I'll work without cheese.

17:25.795 --> 17:27.087
Who is this?

17:27.129 --> 17:29.757
That's Jeremy,

17:27.129 --> 17:29.757
our model for the evening.

17:29.799 --> 17:31.091
That's why I didn't call you.

17:31.133 --> 17:32.677
OTTO:

17:31.133 --> 17:32.677
Francis,

17:32.719 --> 17:35.596
we have already sketched

17:32.719 --> 17:35.596
