18:00.162 --> 18:03.123
Someday, you'll realize

18:00.162 --> 18:03.123
what you turned your back on,

18:03.165 --> 18:04.709
and you will

18:03.165 --> 18:04.709
curse yourself

18:04.751 --> 18:07.336
for your banality

18:04.751 --> 18:07.336
and your shortsightedness,

18:07.378 --> 18:10.840
